title: Lexus/Toyota EU Generation 01 East Europe 2008-2009 ver.1 Navi
description:
Attention!
 
This isn't copy of the official disc! 
Intended for the acquaintance and/or experimental use only! 
Full performance at this time isn't guaranteed!
Map source - from another system (TNS310).

If you don't sure - don't try it!

Otherwise:
1-st - check http://www.lexus-mapupdates.eu/ or http://www.toyota-mapupdates.eu/ site.
2-nd - only if your update set is PZ485-X01EU-08 - you can try this disc, PZ485-X03EU-08 is incompatible.

In any case, if you try to use this sample - please, report here about result. Please, write about car model & year, this can help to another guys (& girls ;-) ).

Thanks in advance!

Big thanks for the idea and links to the source maps to one man from Slovakia!

Map Coverage:
Austria
Belgium
Hungary
Germany
Latvia
Lithuania
Netherlands
Poland
Romania
Slovakia
Croatia
Czech Republic
Estonia

Already reported as worked at:
TLC-120 '04
RX-300  '03 & '04

Known limitation:
Don't show all street name on map, at current & next position only.
Don't show rivers, lakes etc.


North disc is here: https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4862966
South disc is here: https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4867005


I need links to PZ485-X01EU-08 set (marked E01, disc #: 86271-70V981,86271-70V991,86271-70W011) for experimental purpose.
Thanks in advance!
